                  <scopecontent>
                     <p>Autograph fair copy, here untitled, on a slip of paper annotated in
								the hand of <extref href="http://www.thomasgray.org/resources/glnames.shtml#Wharton, Thomas, 1717-1794"
                                show="replace"
                                linktype="simple">
                           <persname normal="Wharton, Thomas, 1717-1794">Thomas
										Wharton</persname>
